INSERT INTO `lar_article` VALUES ('1', '5', '华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元', '', '华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元', '华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元', '/uploads/2018-04-26/20180426093048442.jpg', '<p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15247017159099fcf86830a\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524701739134fea113a40d\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">华为遭<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>司法部调查，或涉</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">违反向伊朗禁运的有关制裁</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">华尔街日报</span>报道,<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>司法部正在调查华为公司是否违反向伊朗禁运的有关制裁。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">华尔街见闻援引<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">知情人士</span>的消息称，在进行上述针对华为的刑事调查以前，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">商务部</span>和<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>财政部外国资产管制办公室已经对华为发出了有关一些制裁问题的行政传票。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">值得注意的是，此前中兴通讯因违反<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>对伊朗制裁条款，被<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">商务部</span>激活拒绝令，未来7年禁止<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>公司向中兴通讯<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">销售</span>零部件、商品、软件和技术。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此前有消息曝出，华为欲在今年退出<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>市场。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">华为高级副总裁余承东此前曾表示：有没有<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>市场，并不阻碍华为成为“世界第一”。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（感受一下，来自王者的蔑视）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524700852284530062e38a\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">特朗普</span>期待与苹果CEO会面：讨论<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>受多国持续不公平对待</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">彭博社</span>，苹果CEO库克在<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>当地时间周三下午在白宫与<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">特朗普</span>会晤。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此前<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">特朗普</span>发推文称，期待与库克的会面，双方将讨论多项议题，包括这么多年来<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>在贸易问题上受到多个国家持续不公平的对待。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">库克方面则在3月份表示，对<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">特朗普</span>提高中国商品<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">关税</span>表示不满，称需要“冷静的头脑”来稳定紧张的关系，避免即将爆发的<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">贸易战</span>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而近期的数据显示，截至周一的三个交易日内，苹果股票价格累计下跌7.1%，致使其市值蒸发639亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>。这波下跌的主要原因是，位于中国台湾的苹果芯片供应商台积电<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">公布</span>的业绩预报弱于先前分析师预期。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（三天失血639亿，库克坐不住了）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">美媒：高通裁员1231人，部分华人竟自愿被炒</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>《<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">世界日报</span>》报道，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>通讯业龙头公司高通（Qualcomm）17日宣布裁员1231人，主要针对高阶主管。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于遣散费高达10个月薪水，华人王姓工程师认为资遣方案十分优渥，因此便提交申请自愿被炒，没想到竟遭上级驳回。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（带上技术回国，大把橄榄枝）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">Facebook</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">公布</span>2018财年一季度财报：净利润同比增63%</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月26日凌晨，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">Facebook</span>今天发布了截至3月31日的2018财年第一季度未经审计财报。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">报告显示，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">Facebook</span>第一季度营收为119.66亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>，比去年同期的80.32亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>增长49%，不计入汇率变动的影响为同比增长42%；净利润为49.88亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>，比去年同期的净利润30.64亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>增长63%。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（小扎憋笑耿直脸：“参议员 我们靠<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">广告</span>赚钱”）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15247009090554442c8685f\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">京东<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">网易</span>股价纷纷创52周新低</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">彭博社</span>报道，今年迄今，中国科技股集体表现不佳，其中京东和<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">网易</span>的股价纷纷在周二创下约52周新低。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去年这个时候，百度股价在中国互联网公司中的表现最差。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当时，阿里巴巴和腾讯的股价在年内均上涨了超过25%，京东的涨幅更是接近34%。百度则只涨了7%。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今年，京东重新陷入了亏损，阿里巴巴和腾讯也阴跌不断。百度的转型故事仍在持续，但投资者尚未被说服，这导致中国科技巨头们集体下挫。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524701757959773f2b3f26\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">马云：想摆脱<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>的控制，中日都要开发自主芯片技术</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">彭博社</span>，阿里巴巴联合创始人马云在日本早稻田大学发表演讲时表示，无论是日本还是中国，都需要发展属于自己的半导体技术，这样才能摆脱<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>对全球芯片市场的控制。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">马云表示，阿里巴巴拥有让芯片产品更“包容”的愿景，希望能够以更廉价、更高效的形式提供给所有人。马云表示在过去的四年中，阿里巴巴已经先后投资了五家半导体公司。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">雷军放大招：小米硬件综合净利润率将不超5%</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日，小米创始人、董事长兼CEO雷军在发布手机<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">新品</span>小米6X后承诺：小米每年整体硬件业务的净利率不超过5%，如超过，将把超过5%的部分用合理的方式返还给小米用户。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看似“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">让利</span>大酬宾”，但也有人称，在国内，5%算是很好的净利润率了。小米特别宣布这个数字，是为了营销，为今年的<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">上市</span>造势。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据媒体报道，小米的硬件利润从来都很低。2016年，小米硬件综合净利润率不过2.8%，而2017年，小米的总利润率预计也只有 6%。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（我们最后是不是还得倒找雷总钱？）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152470050458644dd649530\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">马云对话日本学生：别学比尔盖茨早退学，很少有人成功</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日下午，日本早稻田大学大隈讲堂内，日本学生们不断抛出各种“日宅”式问题，引发阿里巴巴董事局<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">主席</span>马云一起进行了一场大开脑洞的对话。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">马云在交流中表示：不要学比尔盖茨、扎克伯格退学，很少有人能成功。你加入一个创业团队，这和金钱无关，这和生活经验、和变化、和改善别人与自己的生活有关。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152470136946846de1d6930\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524701773440e95bbf249d\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">喜茶完成4亿<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>B轮融资，美团旗下龙珠资本投资</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日，喜茶完成4亿<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>B轮融资，投资方为美团点评旗下龙珠资本。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">龙珠资本创始合伙人朱拥华代表美团出任喜茶董事。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此轮融资是否意味着喜茶“站队”美团？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对此，喜茶创始人聂云宸表示：本轮融资后龙珠资本不是喜茶最大的机构股东。从股份比例来看，喜茶依然由管理团队控股。同时，喜茶方面在合同中明确可以与美团外卖合作，也可以与其他外卖平台合作。反过来也一样，美团点评不会给喜茶流量上的扶持或排他<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">性服务</span>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">沃尔玛120亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>收购Flipkart，软银或至少收入40亿</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">彭博社</span>援引<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">知情人士</span>消息，沃尔玛即将敲定以至少120亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>的价格收购印度电子商务网站Flipkart多数股权，该笔交易可能在未来两周内完成。沃尔玛此轮投资很有可能获得Flipkart大约60%到80%的股权，这也致使后者的估值达到200亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>以上。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另据36氪的消息，此轮收购之后，软银或成最<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">大赢家</span>，至少40亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>收入囊中。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15247013903096583415ac2\" alt=\"华为遭美国司法部调查；受芯片影响，苹果市值3天蒸发639亿美元\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">携程投资超音速飞机制造商，上海飞洛杉矶从12小时变6小时</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日，携程宣布与全球领先的超音速飞机制造商Boom Supersonic（下称“Boom”）达成战略投资。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据了解，携程将基于在中国市场多年的积累，协助Boom与中国航司商谈商业合作以及在航空领域上的发展。双方还表示，期待共同努力推动将中国飞往<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">美国</span>、南亚、大洋洲的飞行时间缩减至目前的一半，也期待未来出行更加便利、高效。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过，携程并没有披露具体的交易金额和交易方式。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">4个月融2轮，作业盒子完成C轮1亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>融资</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月25日作业盒子正式对外宣布，已于今年2月份完成C轮共计1亿美<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>融资，本轮融资由云锋基金领投，好未来等机构跟投，泰合资本担任独家财务顾问。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是作业盒子四个月内完成的第2轮融资，也是成立以来完成的第5轮融资。2017年10月，作业盒子刚刚宣布完成由BAI贝塔斯曼亚洲投资基金领投，新世界集团、好未来、BV百度风投跟投的2亿<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">元</span>人民币B+轮融资。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '1524706250', '', '5');
INSERT INTO `lar_article` VALUES ('2', '3', '空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？', '', '', '央视网消息：这两天，空军组织歼击机、轰炸机、侦察机、预警机开展海上方向实战化训练，轰-6K等战机连续“绕岛巡航”。央视记者在多个现场记录战机航迹，见证空军飞行员“绕岛巡航”全过程。', '', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">弹满舱箭上弦 数架轰-6K依次升空</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152422811098034d5c8a27b\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">记者</span>：“这里是空军某机场，我们可以看到轰-6K战机，弹满舱，箭上弦，正在滑向飞机起飞线。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一大早，参加“绕岛巡航”的空军轰炸机部队官兵进入战位，数架轰-6K战机依次升空。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">歼击机预警机战斗编组向海上进发</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524228110983187fcaeb9b\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与此同时，在华东多个空军机场，参加任务的歼击机、预警机按照战斗编组，陆续起飞。多型战机进入预定航线后，在指定空域按照任务规划，排开阵势，向海上进发。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152422811097781baadb64f\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152422811101065d591df0a\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524228110994f69d1c1dd3\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">飞行同期</span>：“发现不明飞机一批两架，由我机右后方靠近。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">记者</span>：“我现在空军的特种飞机上，由这架战机与多型战机组成的空中编队正在执行‘绕岛飞行’任务。通过舷窗我们可以看到，两架战机正在抵近飞行。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">几分钟后，对方战机脱离消失。据机组人员介绍，像这样的情况，在“绕岛巡航”过程中经常遇到，双方的对峙有时甚至长达几十分钟。但不管对方战机离得多近、做出什么动作，飞行员都会按照计划航线持续飞行。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524228110975d318981b33\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">空军航空兵某师轰-6K机长 翟培松</span>：“面对敌情可以娴熟处置，部队实战化水平在不断提升，我们在海岛以东活动已经成为常态。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经过一上午的海上飞行，完成第一批“绕岛巡航”的战机纷纷返航。随着空军装备更新换代和实战化训练的不断深入，像这样的海上训练，频率越来越高、战机出动的数量和规模也越来越大。</p><p><br/></p>', '1524242463', '1524242463', '栽茜', '0');
INSERT INTO `lar_article` VALUES ('3', '3', '空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？', '', '', '央视网消息：这两天，空军组织歼击机、轰炸机、侦察机、预警机开展海上方向实战化训练，轰-6K等战机连续“绕岛巡航”。央视记者在多个现场记录战机航迹，见证空军飞行员“绕岛巡航”全过程。', '', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">弹满舱箭上弦 数架轰-6K依次升空</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/152422811098034d5c8a27b\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">记者</span>：“这里是空军某机场，我们可以看到轰-6K战机，弹满舱，箭上弦，正在滑向飞机起飞线。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一大早，参加“绕岛巡航”的空军轰炸机部队官兵进入战位，数架轰-6K战机依次升空。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">歼击机预警机战斗编组向海上进发</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1524228110983187fcaeb9b\" alt=\"空军“绕岛巡航”空中飞行同期声曝光 飞行员咋操作？\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与此同时，在华东多个空军机场，参加任务的歼击机、预警机按照战斗编组，陆续起飞。多型战机进入预定航线后，在指定空域按照任务规划，排开阵势，向海上进发。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQu